call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Schroder (BOS) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to DAL.
Smart (BOS) makes hand-on-ball contact to dislodge the ball from Doncic (DAL) on the perimeter.
Williams III (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path and does not deliver contact.
Porzingis (DAL) moves alongside Schroder's (BOS) path and absorbs the body contact before blocking the driving shot attempt.
Williams III (BOS) and Porzingis (DAL) engage and disengage with one another for the loose ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Porzingis (DAL) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to BOS.
Smart (BOS) is already in Brunson's (DAL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Smart (BOS) straddles the lane line and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Porzingis (DAL) moves laterally into Smart's (BOS) path and makes body contact, which affects Smart's SQBR. The contact occurs prior to Smart's gather.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in legal screening position in Smart's (BOS) path and absorbs the contact.
Smart (BOS) makes marginal contact to Doncic's (DAL) arm before dislodging the ball.
Williams III (BOS) deflects the pass attempt to Porzingis (DAL) before incidental contact occurs.
Smart (BOS) extends both hands into Doncic's (DAL) front in the backcourt and affects his SQBR.
Bullock (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Smart's (BOS) path and absorbs the contact.
Doncic (DAL) naturally releases away from Richardson (BOS) during his step-back at the end of his drive.
